OL,3,CProminent loyalist in court over 'call
OL,4,Cto arms' social post
OL,6,FA prominent loyalist allegedly made a
OL,7,Frace-hate social media posting for
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland to be brought to a
OL,9,Fstandstill in a bid to "stop the
OL,10,Fspread of evil Islam", a court heard
OL,11,Ftoday.
OL,13,FPolice claimed the message on David
OL,14,FStitt's Facebook page which urged
OL,15,Fmembers of the public to attend a
OL,16,Fseries of protests was "a call to
OL,17,Farms".
