OL,3,CProminent loyalist in court over 'call
OL,4,Cto arms' social post
OL,6,FIt listed parts of Belfast,
OL,7,FNewtownabbey, Carrickfergus, Larne,
OL,8,FBangor and north Down where protests
OL,9,Fwere to be held on August 3.
OL,11,FThe posting stated: "Please forward
OL,12,Fand share to (as) many people as
OL,13,Fpossible, the aim is to bring the
OL,14,Fcountry to a standstill."
OL,16,FAt all locations the advice was for
OL,17,Fwomen and children to be at the front
OL,18,Fof demonstrations.
