OL,3,CProminent loyalist in court over 'call
OL,4,Cto arms' social post
OL,6,FThe posting continued: "This is about
OL,7,Fall of our families; not about being
OL,8,FBritish or Irish, Orange or Green.
OL,10,F"This is the Christian west under
OL,11,Fsiege when children aren't safe (in)
OL,12,Fthe places we send them to express
OL,13,Fhappiness, joy and fun.
OL,15,F"Government won't help. Police are
OL,16,Fpowerless. Were (sic) will you be?
OL,18,F"And what can you say to your children
OL,19,Fin years to come when we had one
OL,20,Fchance to stop the spread of evil
OL,21,FIslam."
