OL,3,CProminent loyalist in court over 'call
OL,4,Cto arms' social post
OL,6,FStitt was arrested by officers from
OL,7,Fthe PSNI's Paramilitary Crime Task
OL,8,FForce as he arrived at Belfast City
OL,9,FAirport on Thursday.
OL,11,FDefence lawyer Gavin Booth challenged
OL,12,Fthe decision to charge him with the
OL,13,Foffence.
OL,15,FHe insisted his client had only
OL,16,Fforwarded on a post containing no
OL,17,Fthreatening or abusive content and
OL,18,Fwhich had been written by someone else.
