OL,3,CProminent loyalist in court over 'call
OL,4,Cto arms' social post
OL,6,F"This is a copy and paste job, they
OL,7,Fwere not his own words," the solicitor
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FMr Booth also submitted that his
OL,11,Fclient has lawful rights to freedom of
OL,12,Fexpression and to protest.
OL,14,FBut an investigating detective
OL,15,Fresponded: "We feel this is a call to
OL,16,Farms for people to take the law into
OL,17,Ftheir own hands."
