OL,4,Cto arms' social post
OL,6,FOpposing bail, he set out how the
OL,7,FAugust 3 protests led to a surge in
OL,8,Fracially-motivated attacks in
OL,9,Fproperties and businesses across
OL,10,FBelfast.
OL,12,FMr Booth told the court Stitt is an
OL,13,F"influential figure in the community"
OL,14,Finvolved in conflict-resolution
OL,15,Finitiatives and work with members of
OL,16,Fall cultures, including taking a group
OL,17,Fon a trip to the Auschwitz
OL,18,Fconcentration camp memorial site in
OL,19,FPoland.
