OL,6,F"This is just one post... he wasn't
OL,7,Fout on the streets trying to encourage
OL,8,Fviolence," the lawyer added.
OL,10,FBail was denied, however, based on the
OL,11,Frisk of re-offending.
OL,13,FDistrict Judge Steven Keown declared:
OL,14,F"There is no hierarchy of individuals
OL,15,Fwithin the community.
