OL,6,F"People who think there is, or that
OL,7,Fsome religions are evil, are the ones
OL,8,Fwho are the threat to our society, not
OL,9,Fthe hard working people from whatever
OL,10,Fcommunity who peacefully contribute to
OL,11,Four society.
OL,13,F"There is no place in our society for
OL,14,Fpeople who hold this view, they are a
OL,15,Fthreat to the society as we have seen
OL,16,Fover the last three or four weeks."
OL,18,FHe remanded Stitt in custody until
